text: The Mullsjö Mission Covenant Church () is a church building in Mullsjö in Sweden. It belongs to both the Uniting Church in Sweden and the Swedish Alliance Mission. The current building was opened in 1992. It replaced an older building which had been there since 1922. ==References== ==Other websites== *Mullsjö Mission Covenant Congregation Category:Churches in Sweden Category:Mullsjö
